# glost-[LANG]-datasource-[SOURCE_NAME]

[LANGUAGE] language data source using [SOURCE_NAME] [database/API/dictionary].

## Overview

This package provides **raw data access** to [SOURCE_NAME] following the Single Responsibility Principle (SRP). It ONLY queries the data source and returns raw data - it does NOT process or transform data.

### Single Responsibility

✅ **Does:**
- Query [SOURCE_NAME] database/API
- Return raw dictionary entries
- Handle connection and errors

❌ **Does NOT:**
- Apply transcription rules (use transcription system packages)
- Transform or process data (use strategy packages)
- Implement business logic (use adapter/lookup packages)

